Package: NOAA
Type: Package
Title: NOAA Earthquake Geoms and Maps
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Gopal Seshadri
Maintainer: Gopal Seshadri <gopalavarmanseshadri@gmail.com>
Description: It cleans th NOAA data. It has a geom to plot earthquake timelines with magnitude and deaths. It has another geom to add labels to the earthquake plotted. It also has function to create interactive maps.
